I am single mother of 3 who wants to provide my children their basic necessities and good education. I would like to loan the amount of US$3,000.00.  Since November when our company shut down. In fact kids are part of the honor rolls and they took the early exams yesterday. I wrote a promissory note promising to pay the unsettled balance within next week. The money which I am going to loan will be use for my Philippine native products or handicraft e-commerce website. Domain name and hosting payment, buy raw components like shells, starfish, abacca fiber rope, twigs baskets, native home decor and native fashion bags samples for stocks and photo filling purposes, digital camera, pay my dsl bill, pay school and business registration payments. 

I am knocking on your kind heart to help me fund this loan and help us recover from this financial crisis. Helping me fund this loan is the greatest gift you can give to my children's education and their future.

Your kind attention and consideration to this matter is highly appreciated. 

Thank you in advance and God bless!
